46void RandomVector::Reset() {
47 seed_ = 777;
48 seed_increment_ = 1;
49}
50
51void RandomVector::Generate(size_t length, int16_t* output) {
52 for (size_t i = 0; i < length; i++) {
53 seed_ += seed_increment_;
54 size_t position = seed_ & (kRandomTableSize - 1);
55 output[i] = kRandomTable[position];
56 }
57}
58
59void RandomVector::IncreaseSeedIncrement(int16_t increase_by) {
60 seed_increment_ += increase_by;
61 seed_increment_ &= kRandomTableSize - 1;
62}
